{
  "identifier": "@local:",
  "importedTimeStamp": 1776737419181,
  "name": "提取基金数据",
  "operation": {
    "fields": [
      {
        "key": "llm.prediction.systemPrompt",
        "value": "Role: 基金 APP 截图数据提取器专家\nTask: 识别并提取截图中显示的基金持仓关键数据，并严格按照提供的 JSON Schema 格式化输出。\n\nOperational Rules:\n\n纯净输出：禁止输出任何 Markdown 标记（如 ```json）、解释、开场白或结尾语。仅输出合法的 JSON 字符串。\n\n数据完整性：\n\n严禁编造、推理或猜测数据。\n\n若截图中未出现某字段，统一填入 null；仅当截图明确无待确认交易时，transactions 返回空数组 []。\n\n格式约束：\n\n金额/数值：移除千分位逗号（如 1,234.56 转换为 1234.56），保留 2 位小数。\n\n百分比：保留符号（如 + 或 -），以字符串格式输出，示例：+4.83%。\n\n基金代码：固定为 6 位数字字符串。\n\n逻辑区分：\n\n务必区分“持有收益”（累计收益）与“今日收益”（单日变动金额）。\n\n“待确认金额”通常指正在交易中但未计入持仓的资金。\n\n严禁错位映射：\n\ndaily_profit / hold_profit / hold_rate / daily_change / nav / nav_date 只能来自对应字段，不得写入 transactions。\n\ntransactions 仅提取“待确认交易”区域；若截图未出现该区域或未出现交易项，返回空数组。"
      },
      {
        "key": "llm.prediction.structured",
        "value": {
          "type": "json",
          "jsonSchema": {
            "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "properties": {
              "code": {
                "type": [
                  "string",
                  "null"
                ],
                "pattern": "^[0-9]{6}$",
                "description": "6位基金代码"
              },
              "name": {
                "type": [
                  "string",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "基金完整名称"
              },
              "total_amount": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "总金额（元）"
              },
              "hold_amount": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "持有金额（元）"
              },
              "pending_amount": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "待确认金额（元）"
              },
              "cost_price": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "持仓/持有成本价"
              },
              "shares": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "持有份额"
              },
              "daily_profit": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "今日收益（元）"
              },
              "hold_profit": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "持有收益（元）"
              },
              "hold_rate": {
                "type": [
                  "string",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "持有收益率，带正负号百分数"
              },
              "daily_change": {
                "type": [
                  "string",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "日涨幅，带正负号百分数"
              },
              "nav": {
                "type": [
                  "number",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "最新单位净值"
              },
              "nav_date": {
                "type": [
                  "string",
                  "null"
                ],
                "description": "净值更新日期 (MM-DD)"
              },
              "transactions": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "additionalProperties": false,
                  "properties": {
                    "type": {
                      "enum": [
                        "买入",
                        "卖出",
                        "未知",
                        null
                      ]
                    },
                    "amount": {
                      "type": [
                        "number",
                        "null"
                      ]
                    },
                    "expected_date": {
                      "type": [
                        "string",
                        "null"
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                },
                "description": "待确认交易列表"
              }
            },
            "required": [
              "code",
              "name",
              "total_amount",
              "hold_amount",
              "pending_amount",
              "cost_price",
              "shares",
              "daily_profit",
              "hold_profit",
              "hold_rate",
              "daily_change",
              "nav",
              "nav_date",
              "transactions"
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
